name: Alexi Wiseman
description: I am a very cool-headed man… I am a honest and sincere person.. I am the only child of my parents, so I have a very small family.. I like outdoor a great deal.. I enjoy spending time with my partner, especially the beach for a picnic..I am at a place in my life where I am ready to share my life with the right partner. I am a free spirit. I believe that people have the right to live their life as they chose. I am not judgmental and have little tolerance for people who are . I find arrogance and racism to be a complete turn off and I could not see myself with a partner that didn’t share my belief that we are all equal human beings sharing this beautiful world.
